title: Happy Hour #24: SMNTY Takes a Vacation
itunes:title: Happy Hour #24: SMNTY Takes a Vacation
description:
As Anney and Samantha prepare to go on vacation, we dig into vacation stress for women, the difficulty of unplugging and importance of friendships, traditions and relaxing. Basically asking the question...how does one vacate?
